(20, 1, '2014-02-22 17:28:37', '2014-02-22 17:28:37', '<h2>Welcome to ITsterling Training Consulting Development</h2>\r\n<h2>[hr style="1,2,3,4" margin="40px 0px 40px 0px"]</h2>\r\n<strong>ITsterling</strong> use different appearances for developing original &amp; advanced learning ideas. We are always ready to share our professional experience and methodological ability. Located at Delhi-NCR, we specialize in offering effective Consulting &amp; Training Solutions for Java Technology, Embedded System, .Net Technology, Android, PHP Training, SEO and Dataware Housing, to name a few. We possess a team of software engineers &amp; other professionals to undertake expert training courses. The software engineers working with us have a detailed knowledge of current software &amp; tools and offer you the complete professional solutions for all kinds of applications. Reasonable courses with total commitment and dedication are the key to our growth in the market. At ITsterling, our growth can be straightforwardly attributed to our experienced team and planned training material we undertake. Our rates are affordable and the training is results-driven. We assure that the IT Training &amp; Consulting Services provided by us are reliable, effective and career focused. The target of our IT Training Services has not only restricted to acquire knowledge but also to get a good job and a brighter future.\r\n\r\nEvery year, our training programs aid thousands of students. After attending a course, you are capable to apply practices and put the subject matter learned into action. In addition to this, we have all types of facilities, which are needed to render these IT Consulting &amp; Training Solutions. Besides, we hold expertise in providing training &amp; consulting services for SQT, SAS, Red Hat Administration, C/C++ Language, Oracle Skill Set, Synon, SAN and ITIL. It is due to the perfect blend of our advanced methodologies and efficient workforce that we have been able to provide reliable Training Courses. Under the assistance of these professionals, we provide these courses that are probably amongst the best available in Delhi-NCR. ITsterling brings you highly focused and career oriented technical education services with the support of professionals, who have years of years in this domain. Our enterprise holds expertise in providing Training &amp; Consulting Services for Java Technology, Android, PHP Training, Testing(QTP) and many others. These training courses help you to learn how to use several professional consulting methods. Our offered courses are experiential, you learn from "professionals" by being guided to think about and experience the conditions you study.\r\n\r\nThe software engineers &amp; other professionals employed by us make every effort to meet the exact requirements of the students. Our state-of-the-art technologies have helped us to provide these courses in sync with the training industry norms. We have received many honors and are rated as one of renowned Software Training Centers in the city.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2014-09-26 19:25:37', '2014-09-26 19:25:37', '', 0, 'http://itsterling.com/?page_id=20', 0, 'page', '', 0),
