(291, 1, '2014-08-03 09:03:48', '2014-08-03 09:03:48', '<a href="http://itsterling.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/php2.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-282" alt="php2" src="http://itsterling.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/php2-300x152.jpg" width="300" height="152" /></a>\r\n\r\nThere are several famous web applications such as E-Commerce, Online Catalogs, Blog and Web Forms that you must have heard. The dynamic applications have revolutionized the use of internet in its own way. In short, we are discussing the latest technology of dynamic sites that works in accordance with the online visitors and/or the administrators. PHP programming manages these web applications and is the widely popular solution for the dynamic requirements of the e-business worldwide. We, “IT STERLING”, are a top emerging institute for teaching the students to develop their career in web technology and IT field. Being one of the trusted <b>PHP training institutes in Pandav Nagar</b>, we are providing job-oriented courses that will help you grab best job opportunities in the IT field. The range of professional courses provided by us include <b>PHP with MySql Course</b>, Word press Course, CMS training in Joomla Course and Drupal Course. As the course is totally concerned with the web, so students will be having limitless opportunities perform Live Projects of web development.\r\n\r\nThe content and course structure of <b>PHP Training</b> includes the following levels:\r\n\r\n<b>Level 1: Introduction to Internet</b>\r\n\r\nThis level will help you to learn more about the internet.\r\n\r\n• What is Internet and the WWW?\r\n• Introduction to sites and its functionality\r\n• Introduction to HTML/CSS\r\n• Introduction to Web addresses and web hosting\r\n\r\n<b>Level 2: PHP Programming</b>\r\n\r\nThis level includes the complete training in PHP Programming\r\n\r\n• Introduction to PHP\r\n• Taking User Input from Forms via PHP\r\n• Variables and Expressions in PHP\r\n• Conditional Tests